# Large optional audio packs stay local. Required studio loops are tracked
# (see REQUIRED_ASSETS.md) so CI and EAS builds can verify/bundle them.
*.ogg
*.m4a
*.wav

# Ignore ad-hoc mp3 dumps by default…
*.mp3
# …but always track the Sound Studio required set:
!ambient-rain.mp3
!ambient-ocean.mp3
!ambient-forest.mp3
!ambient-wind.mp3
!ambient-fire.mp3
!music-ambient.mp3
!music-drone.mp3
!music-crystal.mp3
